column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.deVRad_u, p.deVRadErr_u, p.deVRad_z, p.deVRadErr_z, p.z, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, g.lgm_tot_p5#  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS g on g.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND g.lgm_tot_p5# > #
